{"tid":391984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇諗過人地可能根本唔care個仔生死","createTime":"2017-09-08T07:48:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T16:16:02.000Z","uid":60231,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"64a010c3e7aaca0e91db401d3dba92416bf2bc6c","tid":391984,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T07:48:24.000Z","msg":"見到佢有報應，作為香港年青人既我當然心涼埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但諗深一層，港共狗官服務得中共，本身就冇人性可言，有冇母愛都成問題<br />\n<br />\n作為港共高官，得1個目標，就係為左自己既利益，或者為左奶共，會用盡一切身邊可用既資源，當然包括有直接血緣關係既生物<br />\n<br />\n分分鐘就算2個仔都瓜埋佢都根本唔care，因為可能只不過係佢既工具黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢係真係care自己個仔，就好難會助紂為虐咁去搞9人地個仔<br />\n<br />\n就好似愛狗既人唔會突登去食狗肉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我地心涼笑柒佢，其實佢可能don't give a shit<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2560e3d2099baf6eabc7c6fcb652119cd966dd67","tid":391984,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T07:51:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9032ccaddd7b067e1acc8ff8387f22d5eddc26e","tid":391984,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T07:52:48.000Z","msg":"689都係咁啦，逼到個女癲癲喪喪<br />\n<br />\n不過關我撚事？"},{"pid":"b442392385e133f9303701be2fd5158cfb85f5f7","tid":391984,"uid":49602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T08:24:52.000Z","msg":"明知個仔有情緒病就擺多d時間陪下佢喇...做乜鳩官丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b0b53e7593b5d695a903ae0b8ab088ce9f1471","tid":391984,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T09:40:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>689都係咁啦，逼到個女癲癲喪喪<br />\n<br />\n不過關我撚事？</blockquote><br />\n冇既，只係覺得笑9佢e樣野對佢冇乜大影響咁解啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla